Name: bthomehub5-devicelist
Version: 0.1.0
Summary: A library that returns a list of devices currently connected to a BT Home Hub 5
Home-page: https://github.com/ahobsonsayers/bthomehub5-devicelist
Author: Arran Hobson Sayers
